description: Try our easy to follow Healthier Pad Thai recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Pad thai,Low saturated fat,Low salt,Tree nut free,Egg free,Healthier Easier,Low sugar,Sesame free,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,High fibre,Quick & easy lunch,Chicken,Low fat,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Healthier Pad Thai Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a large frying pan or wok over high heat. Add garlic, chilli and chicken and stirfry for 2 minutes. Add stir-fry vegetables and soy sauce, and cook for 2-3 minutes, stirring regularly. Toss through noodles and cook for a further 2-3 minutes.
Divide among four plates and top with bean sprouts and coriander. Serve with lime wedges.
